history.content:
Hey Everyone,

I am part of PlexTech, a tech/software consulting club at UC Berkeley, and we're planning to expand our officer team for Spring 2021! We will be including a new Machine Learning Curriculum Officer role, and are looking for Cal students who have taken CS 189 or have in-depth ML industry expertise.

The role requires around 6-8 hours of weekly commitment, and responsibilities include teaching two lessons a week to a small group of students, holding office hours, and tailoring a pre-existing DS/ML curriculum to your individual preferences.

This is a great opportunity if you love data science, machine learning, and/or teaching, and you want to be an officer for a fun club with connections to many interesting startups. Please fill out the form below if you are interested:

https://forms.gle/hK9y9LU72ApXCkg79
history.subject: PlexTech: Looking for ML Enthusiasts!
